&lt;Wilderness Experience Inc>said it may be forced to file for bankruptcy court protection,or seek a liquidation of the company, if it is unsuccessful inobtaining the financing necessary to meet its bank debtcommitments.    The company said it has been unable to renew a short-termborrowing arrangement with its bank or to make scheduled debtpayments.    It also said the bank has said it will foreclose theirsecurity interest in the company if it does not present anacceptable payment program within the next several weeks. Reuter&#3;